t_timestamp",\n    "reason": "Server spans missing during fault period suggests ShippingService pod crash",\n    "suggested_metrics": ["pod_processes", "container_restart_count"],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["shippingservice", "OOMKilled", "exit", "crash"],\n    "critical_timestamp": "2025-06-27 21:10:07"\n  }\n}\n```'}
